<title>O HAPPY DAY!</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw kipah ni, ka huntel ni,
 Nang ka Hukdampa, ka Pathien;
 Ka lunggil nuomsa'n kipak hen,
 A kipahna chuh gen viel hen.

[V2]
 Kipah ni (2) Ka gitloh a silthien ni chuh,
 Kiven leh paucham dan ei hilh;
 Nicheng a kipak zing dingin,
 Kipah ni (2) Ka gitloh a silthien ni chuh.

[V3]
 2. Tatna lopi chuh zawh eitai,
 Kei Lalpa a, Amah kei a;
 Aman ei kai, ka zuizel tai,
 Aw nema A gen zawp dingin.

[V4]
 3. Ka lung liengvai, tun chawldam in,
 Ziehi chawlhna nuom chuh ahi;
 Na Lalpa nusieh ngei ki'n la,
 A kawma thupha tin changin.

[V5]
 4. Ka kitiemna vanah A zai,
 Kitiemna nicheng in zana;
 Ka hinkhuo hi a hungbeih a,
 Thih ding thutiem ka chan gei in.</lyrics>
</song>